lines: Mbe n'obosera bwa Yeso ime yane,
Mbe nobosera bwa Yeso ime yane,
Yes' omwanchi omoy'one, Ancha menye as'ore,
Tontiga inche bweka, obe ang'e botambe,
Omuy' ore Nyasae, Inche tindi n'obuya
Obe ime asende, Emiaka na emiaka.
Kwangir' aye mono, Igw' eriogi bwango
Rend' engaki nenke, Ndero ibaga rire,
Yeso ngoet' are, Yeso ngoet' are,
Yeso ngoet' are, Yeso ngoet' are,
Yeso ngoet' are, Yeso ngoet' are,
Yeso ngoet' are, Yeso ngoet' are,
Tama goch' ase Yes' obe ang'e;
Tindi na ekina n' omosibore nde,
Tori na Mosani onde bun' Ere,
Ne chiira chiao, Kor' ase nde.
And'onsi na Yeso tindi nche bweka.
And'onsi na Yeso tindi nche bweka,
Aye nobe buna Yeso Omochenu pi?
Gose mobaso gati gose ko bwaira,
As' obuya bwa Yeso ntenene aria,
Iruma ria Igoro, Ika korwa Igoro;
Oboe ne chinguru chisonsi chia Iso.
Nomwegene Yeso and' onsi as' ore?;
Bionsi korw' as' Are, naye moe bo,
